# l2.system

minimal initial microkit system description.

components
- l2_core: privileged core that manages systems
- serial: debug output
- example_vector: demonstration workload inside a system

future versions will add more systems and host communication channels.

protection domain l2_core {
    program "build/core.elf"
}

protection domain serial {
    program "build/serial.elf"
}

protection domain example_vector {
    program "build/example_vector.elf"
}

channel l2_core serial
